7</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0722.tlg001:7:23:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Orib.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.23.28</biblScope></bibl>, or (in med. form) <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">-ίσομαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1146.tlg001:3:256\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Antip.Stoic.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.256</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">pf.</tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-πεπόδισμαι</foreign> (v. infr.): (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐν, πούς</etym>):—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put the feet in bonds</tr_>: hence, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put in bonds, fetler</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοὺς</foreign> <pb n=\"547\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μάντιας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:69\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.69</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐμπεποδισμένος τοὺς πόδας</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:60\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">60</biblScope> </bibl>; [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀλιγοδρᾰνίᾳ</foreign>] <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐμπεπ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg003.perseus-grc1:550\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">